; Fixture journal for installment (parcelamento) tests.
; Covers:
;   - one active installment (FOO) overlapping today
;   - one fully-paid installment (OLDIE) that finished before today
;   - one future-only installment (FUTURO) starting after today
;   - two-card stress test: BB-VISA on a different card than the others
;   - isolated tail (HAVAN 4/4): single forecast occurrence, ADR-011 §Negativas
;   - ended-today series (TAILEND): last forecast occurrence == today
;   - pre-journal series (ESCOLA): tag M=10 but only parcel 4 (past one-off)
;     + parcels 9..10 (`~ monthly`) — exercises the §Errata 2026-04-28
;     followup: remaining = future_count, NOT total - paid
;   - ordinary transactions without parcelamento tag (ignored)

2026-01-01 * Opening
    assets:banco                  10000.00
    equity:opening

; Active parcelamento — 5 occurrences total, spanning 2026-01 .. 2026-05.
; With a "today" around mid-2026, all forecast rows are in the past so
; paid = 5. Use a narrower window below to exercise active state.
~ monthly from 2026-03-01 to 2026-08-01
    expenses:moradia:equipamentos          100.00  ; parcelamento: FOO 2/5
    liabilities:cartao:nubank

; Fully-finished parcelamento — 3 occurrences in early 2020.
~ monthly from 2020-01-01 to 2020-04-01
    expenses:outros                         50.00  ; parcelamento: OLDIE 1/3
    liabilities:cartao:nubank

; Future-only parcelamento — all occurrences strictly after 2100-01-01.
~ monthly from 2100-01-01 to 2100-04-01
    expenses:outros                         30.00  ; parcelamento: FUTURO 1/3
    liabilities:cartao:nubank

; Active parcelamento on a SECOND card — exercises card isolation.
; BB-VISA-LIVE: 4 occurrences, spanning 2026-04 .. 2026-07.
~ monthly from 2026-04-01 to 2026-08-01
    expenses:lazer:assinaturas              80.00  ; parcelamento: BB-VISA-LIVE 1/4
    liabilities:cartao:bb-visa

; Isolated tail — only the last installment of a 4-month series exists
; as a forecast row dated in the past (≤ today). Per ADR-011 §Errata
; 2026-04-28 this series is now EXCLUDED from /api/installments because
; it has no future occurrences. The §Negativas trade-off was reversed
; after real-world journals showed phantom comprometido for finished
; series. Past 1..3 were paid on fatura journals not present here.
~ monthly from 2026-04-01 to 2026-05-01
    expenses:moradia:equipamentos          150.00  ; parcelamento: HAVAN 4/4
    liabilities:cartao:nubank

; Pre-journal series — tag M=10 but only one past one-off (parcel 4)
; was lançada and a `~ monthly` covers parcels 9..10. Parcels 5..8 were
; never lançadas in this journal (they happened pre-journal). Per the
; ADR-011 §Errata 2026-04-28 followup, ``remaining`` is the count of
; forecast occurrences strictly after today (= 2), NOT ``total - paid``
; (= 9). ``next_parcel`` is 9 (the next future occurrence's index).
2025-08-15 * Escola Up Goioere parc 4/10
    expenses:educação:filhos              237.50  ; parcelamento: ESCOLA 4/10
    liabilities:cartao:bb-visa

~ monthly from 2026-09-01 to 2026-11-01
    expenses:educação:filhos              237.50  ; parcelamento: ESCOLA 9/10
    liabilities:cartao:bb-visa

; Ordinary transaction (no parcelamento tag) — should be ignored.
2026-01-15 * Supermercado
    expenses:alimentação:supermercado      200.00
    assets:banco
